com.label305.kama

Class AbstractJsonRequester<ReturnType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.label305.kama.AbstractJsonRequester<ReturnType>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonDeleter, JsonGetter, JsonPoster, JsonPutter

    public abstract class AbstractJsonRequester<ReturnType>
extends Object
    An abstract class which can be extended to execute http requests. Handles url, url parameters and headers. Executes the request and parses the result to an object type or a list if necessary.
